	  compatibility to Type 1 font rasterizer that can't do hint
	  replacement.

	* tfm.c, tfm.h:
	  Fixed a bug that calculation of tfm_string_height() was incorrect.
	  ASCII pTeX specific things are put within #ifndef WITHOUT_ASCII_PTEX.

